@mofada Including that animation is great, thanks! There are updates available but I don't think any recent changes would help with this problem.

@scheglov Does locale affect code completion? I notice this is using simplified Chinese. I do observe a slight delay when completing colors but it isn't anything like this (if I understand the animation correctly).

@alexander-doroshko I think this animation is showing the UI becoming non-responsive during completion. Do you have any guesses what could cause that?
